  <summary date="2022-01-11T17:04:32Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Patient Advocate Tracker Act

This bill requires the Office of Patient Advocacy within the Veterans Health Administration to establish an information technology system that allows veterans or their representatives to electronically file a complaint with a patient advocate and review the status of a filed complaint.</summary>
